responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "781DA88C4413463813147F9E096F710E", "He ran off with a group of performers, said he could blend in better with a traveling troupe. Carlin was concerned that he\'d bring the attention of the Court of Cloaks onto the farm, and it seems that, unfortunately for us, he did. Well, he\'s gone now, so you\'d better go too. Get out of here, and good riddance!")
